Description: Implements the Soil Health Management Index (SHMI), a 
    rotation-scale indicator of management intensity and ecological function. 
    The package harmonizes crop windows, expands daily cover and disturbance 
    events, summarizes organic inputs, and computes standardized pillar scores 
    for cover, diversity, disturbance, and biological amendments. Functions 
    support reproducible workflows for research, monitoring, and reporting.
